  "title": "All-Party Parliamentary Group on Bees, Pollinators, and Invertebrates",
  "purpose": "To raise awareness of insect science in Parliament and understand the effects of insect decline on the natural world. To raise awareness of the issues surrounding invertebrates and pollinators, promote their importance for the national economy and natural environment, and highlight pathways to both conservation and growth of insect and pollinator populations.",
